ld a level 21 mage fight?</span><hr size=1> Where should a level 21 mage fight?  I've been in and out of Lake Rathe, great exp and poor-decent loot for my lvl, but im getting bored, and grouping in South Karana is a disaster, too many idiots that don't know how to play.  Suggestions Anyone?  If possible, id like to stay on non-kunark territory for now...  Any guys i could solo that are in zones anyone knows of, I would apppreciate it very much<br>
<br>
<br>
Taeilin lvl 21 mage  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uuinael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Uinael</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#333333>(12/26/00 6:43:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eagleeyeweb.com/eq/uinaelface.gif width=135 height=136></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Where should a level 21 mage fight?</span><hr size=1>  Here is my suggestion that can take you to 29.. <br>
<br>
First few lvls up till 24 are risky, but worth it.. <br>
<br>
Go to Warsilk Woods and head to Dalnir.. in the tunnel to Dalnir, right before the zone there are 5 monkeys there you can fight.. the lvl range is 21-24 I believe.  They don't aggro you, so you can pick off one at a time.<br>
<br>
The way I fought was use earth pet.. cast burnout and DS and send him in.  Now with the higher lvls I realize how nice malise is, so you may want to just malise to pull one to you, and send in pet that way.   After that just burn all your mana nuking and nuking. <br>
<br>
By the end of the fight for the first few lvls, you should be oom and your pet very low health. Every lvl that you get, the monkeys get easier and easier.<br>
<br>
You can see the exp bar move alot after every kill.. so it is definitely worth all the downtime.   Hey.. you can practice your sense heading skill while medding  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Thats how I got mine so high  lol<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
<br>
 <p>--------------<br>
[53 Elementalist] Uinael (Dark Elf) &lt;Blood of the Phoenix&gt;<br>
